init_text:
A woman has been dating guy after guy, but it never seems to work out. She’s unaware that she’s actually been dating the same guy over and over; a shapeshifter who’s fallen for her, and is certain he’s going to get it right this time.

One day,

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: she meets a guy who’s different from all the others:

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: She begins dating him, and everything is going well.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: She's about to tell him how she feels, but suddenly a terrible thought occurs to her and she pushes him away.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: She tells him she'd like to give it a go again as well.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The woman is surprised and relieved that the man's personality hasn't changed at all since they broke up.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The woman is taken back by the revelation and informs him that she's going to go stay with her grandmother for a while to think everything over.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: She wants to give the two of them another try, but she doesn't want to be deceived again.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He told her he was trying to find out what kind of guy she was looking for and found that he wasn't that person.
